{"tid":1725269,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"to割 or not to割, that's NOT the question","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:35.000Z","uid":301715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2c6ce7546a13be72b4dd939523c5f04b8bc6c5","tid":1725269,"uid":301715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"當有人問你對勇武行為割唔割。你只要答：<span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢場運動開始時就講咗&quot;兄弟爬山，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各自努力</span></span>&quot;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">針對</span></strong></span>既無能<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府</strong></span></span>同濫權<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">差佬</span></strong></span>。大家用唔同方式向同一目標。其他人用咩方式唔需要你評論，唔需要你準許。<br />\n當政府大大聲叫市民割席，為既就係轉移視線，令市民鬥市民。為既就令你揀一邊。<br />\n割就話你反對勇武行為，從而分化示威者，令其內鬥同減弱；唔割就話你支持暴力，與社會同市民為敵。<br />\n無論你揀咩，政府都唔會因此改善，差佬都唔會收歛。其實無人想知你點諗，係得政府想你表態等你落入佢圈套。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">大家要堅定不移抗議政府以暴製亂，縱容差佬濫權施暴。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span>"}]}